data.description: REGENTS PARK IS ONE OF THE MOST BEAUTIFUL NEIGHBORHOODS IN UNIVERSITY PARK COUNTRY CLUB. ALL THE HOMESITES ARE WIDE AND IN THE MIDDLE OF REGENTS IS A BEAUTIFUL PARK. THIS MORTON CUSTOM HOME IS ON THE 3RD FAIRWAY WITH A WONDERFUL FAIRWAY AND TREED VIEW, AND THE FRONT OF THE HOME LOOKS ON TO REGENTS PARK. IT IS A GREAT LOCATION!!! DAVID MORTON CUSTOM HOMES DESIGNED TIMELESS HOMES WITH STATELY FRONT ELEVATIONS ACCENTED BY FRONT COLUMNS AND ARCHES, A CIRCULAR DRIVEWAY LEADS TO A SPACIOUS 3 CAR GARAGE. CUSTOM LEADED GLASS FRONT DOORS AND MARBLE ACCENT THE FOYER. HIGH CEILINGS! LARGE GREAT ROOM WITH AN ALL GLASS SLIDER WALL TO ENJOY THE AMAZING FAIRWAY AND TREED VIEW! THE HOME IS BRIGHT WITH LOTS OF LIGHT AS IT IS SOUTH FACING IN THE REAR OF THE HOME. THE BEAUTIFUL KITCHEN HAS CUSTOM CABINETS, STONE COUNTERTOPS AND BACKSPLASH, BREAKFAST BAR, BREAKFAST NICHE WITH A GREAT VISTA. FAMILY ROOM WITH BUILTINS SURROUNDING THE FIREPLACE, DEN, PLUS LARGE ENTERTAINMENT ROOM WITH FULL BAR. ALL BATHROOMS ARE UPDATED! OWNERS RETREAT HAS 2 WIC, A WALK-IN SHOWER PLUS SOAKING TUB. LARGE LANAI, REMOTE SUN SHADE AWNING, LARGE SALT WATER POOL AND SPA, PLUS CONVENIENT POOL BATH. NICE SIZED LAUNDRY ROOM WITH AMPLE CABINETS. WHOLE HOUSE GENERATOR! ROOF SEALED IN 2015. DON'T MISS THIS BEAUTIFUL CUSTOM HOME IN ONE OF UNIVERSITY PARK'S FINEST NEIGHBORHOODS!
